 <!-- The Hook -->
 <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 italic mt-8 mb-4">The days of cluttered bedside tables are over. Today's travelers carry 3+ devices and expect seamless power everywhere.</p>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">The global wireless charging market is projected to reach <strong>$403.9 billion by 2034</strong> (CAGR 18.3%), with hospitality as a key growth vertical. Competitors like Nonstop Products have already deployed charging solutions in over <strong>500,000 hotel rooms</strong> globally. According to <strong>J.D. Power 2025 North America Hotel Guest Satisfaction Index (NAGSI)</strong>, room amenities and technology are now top drivers of guest satisfaction, with hotels offering integrated charging seeing <strong>15-30% satisfaction lifts</strong>.</p>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Note that the EU <strong>Common Charger Directive 2022/2380</strong> mandates USB-C across all member states from December 2024, directly impacting hotel charger procurement compliance for European properties. At WOWOHCOOL, we build GaN chargers and Qi2-certified wireless solutions designed for the hospitality industry.</p>

 <!-- GEO Quick Answer -->
 <div class="bg-brandBlue/5 border-l-4 border-brandOrange p-5 rounded-r-xl mb-6">
