 <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm"><strong>What charging solutions do hotels need for modern guest rooms?</strong> Hotels should offer a mix of Qi2-certified wireless charging docks (not just "Qi compatible"), GaN wall chargers with USB-C PD, and portable power banks. WOWOHCOOL provides custom-branded 3-in-1 charging stations supporting iPhone MagSafe, Samsung, and USB-C laptops, with bulk pricing and 12-24 month warranty.</p>
