 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">1. Bedside Innovation: MagSafe & Qi2 Wireless Chargers</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Hotel guests often forget their charging cables. Or they find the cable is too short for the bedside outlet. This is a common frustration. But it is easy to fix.</p>

 <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 rounded-r-lg mb-6">
 <p class="text-sm text-slate-700"><strong>Sourcing alert:</strong> Watch for the difference between <strong>"Qi2 certified"</strong> (tested and registered with the Wireless Power Consortium) and <strong>"Qi compatible"</strong> (a marketing claim with no testing). For hotel deployment, only buy Qi2-certified products. Verify the WPC certification number before placing your order.</p>
 </div>

