 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
 <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 uppercase mb-4">Common Issues and Solutions</h3>
 <div class="space-y-4">
 <div class="border-l-4 border-red-400 pl-4">
 <p class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">Charger not powering on</p>
 <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Check outlet connection, verify power adapter is properly seated, test with guest device to confirm</p>
 </div>
 <div class="border-l-4 border-yellow-400 pl-4">
 <p class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">Slow charging speed</p>
 <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Ensure device is Qi-compatible, remove thick cases, clean charging surface, verify adapter wattage</p>
 </div>
 <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">
 <p class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">Device overheating</p>
 <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Remove device immediately, allow cooling, check for foreign objects, verify vent clearance</p>
 </div>
 <div class="border-l-4 border-slate-400 pl-4">
 <p class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-sm">Physical damage</p>
 <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Replace unit immediately with spare, log damage for supplier warranty claim</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

